{
  "stem": "3277.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I still was afraid, but East Germany was still communist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then we crossed East Germany-- went through the West Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Even a West German soldier said to me, have a-- nice trip.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then we came to the-- to the-- you know, like you go to Staten Island-- how do you call it--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ferry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took that-- that last car, put into the ship, which have railroads, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was so thirsty, because he gave me salami, bread, chocolate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was afraid to go into the restaurant, because-- you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I left everything, and I went on the ship.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was very happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes, and also the guy told me that, at the-- at the sea, somebody-- two people who wait for me and will say, [NON-ENGLISH], which means those guys who will take care of me, because I am in Sweden already.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they gave me some chocolate, flowers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They said, listen, you're going to Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It won't be such easy life, but we got you out of Poland, from the system.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they said, this will take a whole night until you'll get to Stockholm.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's a long way from there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in Stockholm, some other people will wait for you, and say some signals.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then, if they say that signal, go to them, and be with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, of course, again, the whole night I slept.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I got those people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They took me immediately to a hotel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't have any identifications.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He said-- one day they told me, you know, we will go to a store, to a five-, ten-cent store, take a picture, and give you some ID card.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
